<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Home | Climate Solutions</title>
  <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: '/' }) %>

  <!-- Hero / Explore Projects -->
  <section class="hero bg-base-200 py-12">
    <div class="hero-content flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Climate Solutions</h1>
      <p class="max-w-xl">
        Discover a meticulously selected group of projects devoted to climate adaptation and mitigation.
      </p>
      <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Projects</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Projects -->
  <main class="container mx-auto py-8 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1: Abandoned Farmland Restoration -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg"
            alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration"
          />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
          <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Alternative Cement -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg"
            alt="Alternative Cement"
          />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
          <p>Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon dioxide; reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of metric tons each year.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Bicycle Infrastructure -->
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg"
            alt="Bicycle Infrastructure"
          />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
          <p>Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and efficient cycling, reducing the need for fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
